
Ranger Help for: enemy dog
==========================

SUMMARY:
Choosing dog means your Ranger specializes against wolves, hounds, jackals,
feral dogs, and similar pack hunters.

This is a broad predator choice that can matter in forests, plains,
swamps, deserts, mountains, arctic lands, and underground areas.

COMMAND:
  setenemy dog

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and terrains
